    "description": "Grimblestone is a point and click, FMV adventure game that sends you on a fantastical journey through the miniature and magical world world of Grimblestone. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192810/extras/4032cd62efdd31d7aa541219102ddd88.poster.avif?t=1752875200\" width=512 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192810/extras/4032cd62efdd31d7aa541219102ddd88.webm?t=1752875200\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192810/extras/4032cd62efdd31d7aa541219102ddd88.mp4?t=1752875200\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>A BIG adventure in a tiny world awaits - </strong><br>When a mysterious artifact shrinks you down to the size of an acorn, you must journey through the miniature &amp; magical world of Grimblestone. A mystical place full of puzzles, riddles, games and adventure, plus a whole host of Grimblings to befriend. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192810/extras/be0e12f5e99647c2791f688613e90781.poster.avif?t=1752875200\" width=430 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192810/extras/be0e12f5e99647c2791f688613e90781.webm?t=1752875200\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192810/extras/be0e12f5e99647c2791f688613e90781.mp4?t=1752875200\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Explore the mysterious and tiny world of Grimblestone -</strong><br>Hidden amongst the flowers, toadstools, tall grass and moss, just beneath the shade of the undergrowth; a hidden world is waiting to be discovered full of  puzzles, mystery, music and more...<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192810/extras/539cb52763b05ce07a9791dd8a3e7c09.poster.avif?t=1752875200\" width=718 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192810/extras/539cb52763b05ce07a9791dd8a3e7c09.webm?t=1752875200\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192810/extras/539cb52763b05ce07a9791dd8a3e7c09.mp4?t=1752875200\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Meet the locals -</strong><br>Grimblestone is a bustling little place, full of friendly Grimblings to meet. Some of which may just hold the key to help you find your way back home.<br><br><strong>A puzzling adventure awaits -</strong><br>Much more lies beneath the surface of Grimblestone. Help solve mysterious puzzles, musical mysteries and try your hand at cards with a Grimbling, to find the clues to return home.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192810/extras/8a0472f8502a53c960811f628301e817.poster.avif?t=1752875200\" width=572 height=322 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192810/extras/8a0472f8502a53c960811f628301e817.webm?t=1752875200\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192810/extras/8a0472f8502a53c960811f628301e817.mp4?t=1752875200\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>A familiar, yet mysterious world -</strong><br>Combining real world images, video, hand drawn illustrations and animation. Grimblestone's world is a mixed media collage of real life and fantasy, where there is always something new to see and experience.<br><br><strong>The bottom of your garden may not seem far from home, but it's a very long way from Grimblestone.</strong>",
